<bibRefCitation box="[1053,1376,1302,1327]" pageId="12" pageNumber="487" refId="ref20841" refString="Mozaffarian, F. &amp; Wilson, M. R. (2016) A checklist of the leafhoppers of Iran (Hemiptera: Auchenorrhyncha: Cicadellidae). Zootaxa, 4062 (1), 1 - 63. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4062.1.1" type="journal article">Mozaffarian &amp; Wilson 2016</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="12.[151,1437,1122,1363]" box="[199,984,1338,1363]" pageId="12" pageNumber="487">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,342,1338,1363]" pageId="12" pageNumber="487">Conclusion:</emphasis>
The pest status of the species needs to be studied in Iran.
</paragraph>
